{
  "stem": "6900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we noticed that a couple of the machines that we were in front of came from Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a-- it must've been a manager sitting at a desk, and they put us one behind the other on these machines.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The SS women with the dogs were still with us-- not the men.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And just interrupting that walking to the mine shaft, they used to sing all their songs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So-- and it was dark at 5 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we used to try and remember the name of the stars that you learned at school just to keep our sanity for the children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, that we didn't know where they were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got down there, we were put behind these electric machines thinking, I suppose, being in this group, we knew about electric machines.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were making munitions there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, they put us behind, and we had to start the-- whatever we made wasn't right, so we were scared.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But before us, there was a group of men-- not Jewish-- brought in to work from different countries.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they made these things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when they realized that we couldn't do it, they left good ones behind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And put the-- and next to us was a cabinet with all shelves with, I suppose, the materials in them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we used to put what we did wrong under there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the woman gave me the wallet back, and one of us used to take care of it every day and put it under there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we thought it was getting too risky, so we didn't have toilets in the camp itself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had latrines.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
